COVID 19 county time series predictions

Simon Brewer

9/29/2020

library(ggpubr)
library(dplyr)
library(lubridate)
# load("covid19new.RData")
preds <- read.csv("COVID19_tests_pred_ranger.csv")
preds$date <- ymd(preds$date)

King County, WA

Where the first case was reported.

fips = 53033
preds.sub <- preds %>% 
  filter(FIPS == fips)
ggline(preds.sub, x = "date", y = "pred")

Westchester County, NY

The epicenter of the disease for a long time

fips = 36119
preds.sub <- preds %>% 
  filter(FIPS == fips)
